p><p>The engineers have finally come up with three subtly different designs, that are each compatible with different fixed and dropper seatposts:</p><ul><li>Type 1: OneUp V2, Fox Transfer (2019), PNW Loam</li><li>Type 2: RockShox Reverb Stealth, X Fusion Manic, SDG Tellis</li><li>Type 3: Fox Transfer (2021) featuring unique barrel nuts</li></ul><figure id=\"attachment_263182\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-263182\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/28092658/aenomaly-switchgrade-saddle-angle-adjust-oneup-v2-dropper-seat-post.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/28092658/aenomaly-switchgrade-saddle-angle-adjust-oneup-v2-dropper-seat-post.jpg\" alt=\"switchgrade with oneup v2 dropper post\" width=\"1200\" height=\"418\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/28092658/aenomaly-switchgrade-saddle-angle-adjust-oneup-v2-dropper-seat-post.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/28092658/aenomaly-switchgrade-saddle-angle-adjust-oneup-v2-dropper-seat-post-297x103.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/28092658/aenomaly-switchgrade-saddle-angle-adjust-oneup-v2-dropper-seat-post-800x279.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/28092658/aenomaly-switchgrade-saddle-angle-adjust-oneup-v2-dropper-seat-post-120x42.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/28092658/aenomaly-switchgrade-saddle-angle-adjust-oneup-v2-dropper-seat-post-768x268.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/28092658/aenomaly-switchgrade-saddle-angle-adjust-oneup-v2-dropper-seat-post-696x242.j